OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry night with any areas of cloud
OL,7,Fclearing to leave largely clear skies,
OL,8,Fwhich will give late sunshine in the
OL,9,Fevening. Overnight, a few mist and fog
OL,10,Fpatches may form inland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny isolated mist and fog
OL,13,Fpatches will be quick clear leaving a
OL,14,Fdry day with light winds and
OL,15,Fpredominantly clear skies giving
OL,16,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling warm in
OL,17,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
